modName: More Damage For Woodcutter's Axe and Pickaxe
summary: This mod will increase damage for woodcutters axe and for the pickaxe.
descriptionHtml:
Hi, this is a mod will increase damage for woodcutter's axe and for the pickaxe.

[color=red]Summary[/color]
I. Description
II. Requirement
III. Installation
IV. Uninstall
V. Changelog

[color=red]I. Description[/color]
This will increase damage for woodcutter's axe and for the pickaxe, they do 11 base damage now.
There are two versions, one english and one french.

[color=red]II. Requirement[/color]
- [color=red]Last version[/color] of skyrim. (not tested on other version)
[color=red]III. Installation[/color]
Use NMM.
Or extract in [color=red]Skyrim/Data[/color]

[color=red]IV. Uninstall[/color]
Use NMM.
Or delete AxeAndPickaxe.esp

[color=red]V. Changelog[/color]
1.00 : Release
author: WildDeer
